{"tid":1182214,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國球迷攻陷韓國大使館微博 : 你們國民能否有點教養","createTime":"2019-06-02T04:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T03:36:27.000Z","uid":109743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff95dca54c69197f0da58ae1ba364bb75816c226","tid":1182214,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"熊貓杯上，韓國男足在領獎後腳踩獎杯的行為引起了中國球迷的強烈不滿。事後，很多球迷來到韓國駐華大使館官方微博下留言，怒斥韓國球員的這種行為。<br />\n<br />\n部分中國球迷留言稱：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;韓國人腳踩熊貓盃獎杯！老子對天發誓，與韓國足球不共戴天！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;贏了就贏了，競技體育。韓國足球青年隊在熊貓杯過後對待獎杯的行為，有違體育精神，那位球員應該出來道歉。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;請韓國大使館對U18球員腳踩獎杯一事給出解釋，不然我強烈要求將這些運動員驅逐出境，並將大使館人員驅逐出境。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你們的國民能不能有點教養？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你們韓國人素質真差，代表國家的足球隊一群野蠻人竟能做出如此禽獸之事&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n有意思的是，在此前的2018年韓國平昌冬奧會上，很多中國體育迷就因為不滿韓國隊的小動作，來到韓國駐華大使館微博下留言怒斥。"},{"pid":"250c7d0c4f8a38e30dfd4bc678e361b0dfd31f9c","tid":1182214,"uid":204306,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;你們的國民能不能有點教養？&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a80f3fae38d3ccf945932987d374a5099584be","tid":1182214,"uid":244137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f689a052933f2e3a90a4224a3ba9fb8ee5a7d284","tid":1182214,"uid":35914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"韓狗話：有本事你咪扮一次痾尿囉，不過你要拎到冠軍先喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c70454a0cb012237eb7f4efe7399d61bdfabc8","tid":1182214,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}